{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"伸缩容器","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flex_Container","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>定义一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flexbox\">flexbox</a>（伸缩盒布局），需要在一个父级元素上使用<code>display</code>属性的值：<code>flex</code>或<code>inline-flex</code>。这个父级元素将成为<strong>flex container</strong>（伸缩容器），而它的所有子元素将变成<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flex_Item\">flex item</a>（伸缩项）。</p>\n<p>使用<code>flex</code>值能将元素渲染成为一个块级容器，而使用<code>inline-flex</code>值则是渲染成一个行内伸缩容器。这些值会将元素格式化，产生<strong>flex formatting context</strong>（伸缩格式化上下文），这类似于块的格式化上下文，而浮动不会干扰容器，且容器的 margins（所有边距）不会随着这些项目被折叠。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性参考","title":"属性参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-content\"><code>align-content</code></a> 行侧轴对齐方式</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-items\"><code>align-items</code></a> 项目自身侧轴对齐方式</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex\"><code>flex</code></a> 伸缩性</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a> 伸缩流</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-flow\"><code>flex-flow</code></a> 伸缩流与换行</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-wrap\"><code>flex-wrap</code></a> 伸缩 - 换行</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content\"><code>justify-content</code></a> 主轴对齐</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸阅读","title":"延伸阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide（CSS 伸缩盒子指南）: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Flexbox\">Basic Concepts of Flexbox</a>（伸缩盒子的基本概念）</em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide（CSS 伸缩盒子指南）: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Aligning_Items_in_a_Flex_Container\">Aligning items in a flex container</a>（伸缩容器里的项目对齐方式）</em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide（CSS 伸缩盒子指南）: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Mastering_Wrapping_of_Flex_Items\">Mastering wrapping of flex items</a>（掌握伸缩项如何进行换行）</em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"定义一个flexbox（伸缩盒布局），需要在一个父级元素上使用display属性的值：flex或inline-flex。这个父级元素将成为flex container（伸缩容器），而它的所有子元素将变成flex item（伸缩项）。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Flex Container","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Flex Container","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Conteneur flexible","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Flex コンテナ","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"플렉스 컨테이너","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/flex_container","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/flex_container/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flex_Container","title":"伸缩容器"}],"pageTitle":"伸缩容器 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}